Package: mpt2irt
Type: Package
Title: Using Multinomial Processing Tree Models to do Item Response Theory
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-24
Author: Daniel W. Heck, Hansjoerg Plieninger
Maintainer: Daniel W. Heck <heck@uni-mannheim.de>
Depends: runjags, rjags, rstan, parallel
Description: Fitting hierarchical MPT models to obtain IRT estimates for different response processes. At the moment, only response style models are implemented (separating bias towards middle category, extreme responding, and acquiesence). Requires the MCMC samplers JAGS and/or Stan.
License: GPL-2
